'''Spinglass''' was a substance naturally created by the [[Killik/Legends|Killiks]] resembling glass and used for a variety of purposes. One such purpose put to use by the [[Gorog|Dark Nest]] was the creation of a billion models of the [[Millennium Falcon/Legends|''Millennium Falcon'']] and [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker's]] [[T-65 X-wing starfighter/Legends|X-wing]] to be sold to citizens of the [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]] and given as gifts to members of the [[Fifth Fleet (Galactic Alliance)|Fifth Fleet]]. However, the models were actually delivery devices for clusters of tiny Gorog assassins.

